--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
OPEN BIO-DATA SOURCES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PaperTrail consumes public biomedical data sources, each under its own terms:
Open Targets (CC0), GWAS Catalog, ClinVar, ChEMBL (CC BY-SA 3.0), PharmGKB
(CC BY-SA 4.0), openFDA / FAERS, PubTator, PubMed / NCBI E-utilities,
ClinicalTrials.gov, and OpenAlex. PaperTrail records each source's license and
access timestamp in its data-source provenance registry.
